header.gameNote: ROSE BOWL GAME PRES. BY NORTHWESTERN MUTUAL

videos.description: On the first snap of the Rose Bowl Game presented by Northwestern Mutual, Stanford's Kevin Hogan hits Christian McCaffrey who does the rest, going 75 yards to the end zone putting the Cardinal up 7-0 early.
videos.headline: McCaffrey in the end zone after one play

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey run for 22 yds to the Iowa 47 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: C. McCaffrey run for 22 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Stanford's Kevin Hogan keeps the ball himself on the sweep left and easily finds the end zone to increase Stanford's early lead to 14-0.
videos.headline: Hogan runs in untouched for another Stanford TD

videos.description: Stanford's Quenton Meeks jumps in front of the route and picks off Iowa's C.J. Beathard, returning the ball 67 yards the other way to the house, pushing the Cardinal's first quarter lead to 21-0.
videos.headline: Stanford continues dream start with pick-six

videos.description: Already with a receiving touchdown, Stanford's Christian McCaffrey takes a punt return 63 yards to the end zone to increase the lead to 28-0.
videos.headline: McCaffrey scores 2nd TD, this time on a punt return

videos.description: Stanford gets tricky on a designed play when Kevin Hogan fakes fumbling the ball to freeze the safety and then hits Michael Rector for the 31-yard touchdown to continue the rout of Iowa at 35-0.
videos.headline: Hogan fakes fumble, then fires for second TD pass

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey run for 30 yds to the Iowa 18 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: C. McCaffrey run for 30 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: TEAM run for a loss of 19 yards to the Stanf 25 TEAM fumbled, recovered by Stanf Alex Robinson
videos.headline: TEAM run for -19 yds,TEAM fumbled, recovered by Stanf A. Robinson

videos.description: Alex Robinson punt for 42 yds , Desmond King returns for 38 yds to the Stanf 31
videos.headline: A. Robinson punt for 42 yds,D. King returns for 38 yds

videos.description: Iowa's C.J. Beathard finds Matt VandeBerg for the 36-yard catch and run to get the Hawkeyes into the end zone for the first time in the game.
videos.headline: Iowa finds the end zone for the first time

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey run for 25 yds to the Iowa 39 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: C. McCaffrey run for 25 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Kevin Hogan pass intercepted, touchback. Josey Jewell return for no gain
videos.headline: K. Hogan pass intercepted, touchback.,J. Jewell return  for 0 yds

videos.description: Iowa's Akrum Wadley is left wide open and makes the catch and run to the end zone from 31 yards out to cuts Stanford's lead to 38-16.
videos.headline: Wadley scores from 31 yards out

videos.description: Stanford's Kevin Hogan airs it out to Michael Rector for the 42-yard pitch and catch for the score to increase the Cardinal's lead to 45-16.
videos.headline: Rector punctuates win with 42-yard TD
